  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Panelka is a relaxing simulation game filled with warmth and nostalgia, which will take you back to the cozy times of childhood and youth. In it, you will arrange a post-Soviet apartment with furniture and items, creating a familiar cozy atmosphere for many. The game gives you the chance to explore the details of the past, revisit old memories, and once again feel the joy and carefree spirit of those years while creating your creative space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/60641d01547bb833505e22f12119cf9b.poster.avif?t=1762700184\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/60641d01547bb833505e22f12119cf9b.webm?t=1762700184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/60641d01547bb833505e22f12119cf9b.mp4?t=1762700184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have access to classic apartment layouts from the late 80s and early 90s – from Khrushchyovkas to panel buildings. Choose your favorite option and place the furniture however your heart desires – there are no restrictions. If something doesn't fit, easily move items to any place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/751f4a21a51b96e3373f300195dea934.poster.avif?t=1762700184\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/751f4a21a51b96e3373f300195dea934.webm?t=1762700184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/751f4a21a51b96e3373f300195dea934.mp4?t=1762700184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers a huge selection of wallpapers and paints for the walls. Create unique combinations, experiment with colors, or choose stylish brick walls. Everything depends on your imagination!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Photo mode – take atmospheric screenshots and desktop wallpapers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Absence of a game 'grid'.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cozy atmosphere of the 90s.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A large selection of Soviet and post-Soviet furniture, paintings, posters, and various decorative elements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Some elements of the game are created using AI and edited in Photoshop.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Panelka is a relaxing simulation game filled with warmth and nostalgia, which will take you back to the cozy times of childhood and youth. In it, you will arrange a post-Soviet apartment with furniture and items, creating a familiar cozy atmosphere for many. The game gives you the chance to explore the details of the past, revisit old memories, and once again feel the joy and carefree spirit of those years while creating your creative space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/60641d01547bb833505e22f12119cf9b.poster.avif?t=1762700184\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/60641d01547bb833505e22f12119cf9b.webm?t=1762700184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/60641d01547bb833505e22f12119cf9b.mp4?t=1762700184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have access to classic apartment layouts from the late 80s and early 90s – from Khrushchyovkas to panel buildings. Choose your favorite option and place the furniture however your heart desires – there are no restrictions. If something doesn't fit, easily move items to any place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/751f4a21a51b96e3373f300195dea934.poster.avif?t=1762700184\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/751f4a21a51b96e3373f300195dea934.webm?t=1762700184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376760/extras/751f4a21a51b96e3373f300195dea934.mp4?t=1762700184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers a huge selection of wallpapers and paints for the walls. Create unique combinations, experiment with colors, or choose stylish brick walls. Everything depends on your imagination!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Photo mode – take atmospheric screenshots and desktop wallpapers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Absence of a game 'grid'.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cozy atmosphere of the 90s.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A large selection of Soviet and post-Soviet furniture, paintings, posters, and various decorative elements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Some elements of the game are created using AI and edited in Photoshop.</i></p>",
